Name: Overload Field
Description: The opponents ignore Matrix, and when in Matrix, Dodge Gauge bar will restored to full and remain full.

Name: Dangerous Operation
Description: Your team members will receive 100% more damage. And the enemies' HP will be significantly increased.

Name: Energy Destruction
Description: Your team members gain 20% DMG Reduction. And every time they receive damage, their Dodge Gauge bar will be reduced.

Name: Extreme Exchange
Description: Your basic attacks will cost you 1% Max HP and deal additional True DMG equal to 300% the value consumed to your targets.
